             was indicted for <rs id="t17970111-28-off172" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17970111-28-off172" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17970111-28-off172" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17970111-28-cd173" type="crimeDate">6th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970111-28-off172 t17970111-28-cd173"></join>, a linen handkerchief, value Is. three linen shirts, value 7s. 6d. three muslin neckcloths, value 6s. a cotton waistcoat, value 5s. a pair of cotton stockings, value Is, and a cotton night-cap, value 6d, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17970111-28-victim342" type="victimName">
                           Robert 
                           Tomkins
                        <interp inst="t17970111-28-victim342" type="surname" value="Tomkins"></interp>
