                  ; three linen shirts, value 7s. 6d. two cotton night-caps, value 6d a pair of cotton stockings, value 1s. six linen handkerchiefs, value 6s. a diaper breakfast cloth, value Is. and two diaper table-cloths, value 4s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17970111-28-victim344" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Carter
